\id SNG Kyaka Enga Shorter Bible, SF codes August 20, 93 
\h KENANE SOLOMONEME PIYA 
\toc1 KENANE SOLOMONEME PIYA 
\toc2 Kenane Solomeneme Piya 
\toc3 Sol 
\mt1 KENANE SOLOMONEME PIYA  
\ip Pii dakena pyasi palamo doko kiŋi Solomoneme kenane lapo piya. Piyamopa akali mendeme enda kando lamaiyuo kenane pilyamope dee enda mendeme akali kando lamaiyuo kenane pilyamope dopa piya Solomoneme.  
\ip Juu wambu dupwame kenane dupwa suu pyao polo leyami. Kenane dupwa akali endape role pyao mona reto karengenyili pyuo Anatu banya wambu dupwa pipya mona reto role pyao karapengele. Dopa pyuo polo leyaminyi doko Kurisene wambu opetaeko Yesu banya Elyambu Pingi wambu dupwamoo lao suu pyao kareyami.  
\c 1  
